name: CriptoBurguer's Halloween
description: It was a cold night, and some dark energy walked around CriptoBurguer... Our chef got crazy! He spoke some words in a strange language "Arhkmur Vindet Grospinkulum Ontares Kiarat" And an evil voice echoed in the place with a flash of a red light. An then am evil pumpkin appears and, inside it... A Burger Combo... May the spirits protect us.
